# Week 5 - Neural Networks for Vision Tasks

## Dataset Setup

Download CIFAR-10 (Python version) from https://www.cs.toronto.edu/~kriz/cifar.html and place it as:

```
data/
  cifar-10-batches-py/
    batches_meta
    data_batch_1
    data_batch_2
    data_batch_3
    data_batch_4
    data_batch_5
```

## How to Run

1. **Install dependencies**
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```

2. **Run each script**
   ```bash
   python image_captioning.py       # RNN captioning       → captioned_image.png
   python attention_captioning.py   # Attention captioning → attention_captioned_image.png
   python image_gradients.py        # Saliency + confusion → saliency_map.png, confusion_matrix.png
   python style_transfer.py         # Style transfer       → style_transfer_result.png
   ```